In some [[team sport]]s, an '''attacker''' is a specific type of player, usually involved in aggressive play. Heavy attackers are, usually, placed up front: their goal is to score the most possible points for the team.

In [[association football]], attackers are also referred to as [[Forward (association football)#Striker|strikers]].

